posts.post_title: Want to Trade: My E93's for T206 HOF
posts.post_content:
Posted By: Jeff W.
I want to make some progress on my T206 set and am ending my pursuit of the E93 set. These E93's were acquired over the last two years through several auction houses and ebay. I am looking for T206 HOF's in PSA 2-3/ SGC equivalent. I am not looking for anybody specific but I need most such as all three Matty's. all Cobb's, Young's, etc. Just send me an email with what you have available and we can make a deal.

Thanks for looking

Jeff
jwilliams81@mac.com
